OL,3,C'It's blocking the sun': Huge fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out in industrial park
OL,6,FFire crews are tackling a large fire
OL,7,Fin a factory building - with reports
OL,8,Fthat chemicals and oil drums are
OL,9,Fstored nearby.
OL,11,FPictures show smoke rising from a
OL,12,Fbuilding which is at an industrial
OL,13,Fpremises on Clarence Avenue in
OL,14,FTrafford Park.
OL,16,FLocals have been advised to keep their
OL,17,Fdoors and windows closed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
