PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777043470
OL,3,C'It's blocking the sun': Huge fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out in industrial park
OL,6,FSue Harrison owner of local business
OL,7,FCH Motors said: "There's massive
OL,8,Famounts of smoke and stuff falling to
OL,9,Fthe ground.
OL,11,F"We're stuck at work, it's disgusting,
OL,12,Fmy eyes are stinging, my throat's
OL,13,Fhurting.J"A big piece of metal came
OL,14,Fout of the sky and almost hit me."
OL,16,FChelsea Partington, an employee at
OL,17,Fnearby business John's Diner said:
OL,18,F"It's black smoke, it's blocking the
OL,19,Fsun it's that black.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777043470
OL,3,C'It's blocking the sun': Huge fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out in industrial park
OL,6,F"There's cars everywhere and lots of
OL,7,Fpolice and ambulances it's not looking
OL,8,Fgood. I want to go home."
OL,10,FShe said they have not been told
OL,11,Fanything by the police or fire service
OL,12,Fyet, but they are closing the business
OL,13,Ffor the day.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,16,FFire and Rescue Service said: "Just
OL,17,Fafter 1.25pm on Friday 24 April, fire
OL,18,Fcrews were called to reports of a
OL,19,Flarge fire at an industrial premises
OL,20,Fon Clarence Avenue in Trafford Park.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777043470
OL,3,C'It's blocking the sun': Huge fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out in industrial park
OL,6,F"Fire engines from Stretford, Eccles
OL,7,Fand Manchester Central were among the
OL,8,Ffirst to attend the scene, where
OL,9,Ffirefighters found a significant fire
OL,10,Finvolving part of a factory building,
OL,11,Fwith reports that chemicals and oil
OL,12,Fdrums were stored nearby.
OL,14,F"Crews quickly deployed jets to fight
OL,15,Fthe fire, while additional fire
OL,16,Fengines, specialist equipment and an
OL,17,Faerial appliance were also mobilised.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777043470
OL,3,C'It's blocking the sun': Huge fire
OL,4,Cbreaks out in industrial park
OL,6,F"Firefighters continue to work closely
OL,7,Fwith Greater Manchester Police, North
OL,8,FWest Ambulance Service, and Hazardous
OL,9,FArea Response Teams (HART) to manage
OL,10,Fthe incident safely.
OL,12,F"Members of the public are advised to
OL,13,Favoid the area while crews continue to
OL,14,Ftackle the fire and make the scene
OL,15,Fsafe."
OL,17,FIt has been reported that part of
OL,18,FAshburton Road West near Broadoak
OL,19,FIndustrial Estate has been closed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
